control_data.pg_buffercache.control:
# pg_buffercache extension 
comment = 'examine the shared buffer cache' 
default_version = '1.3' 
module_pathname = '$libdir/pg_buffercache' 
relocatable = true 
trusted=true

control_data.anon.control:
# PostgreSQL Anonymizer (anon) extension 
comment = 'Data anonymization tools' 
default_version = '1.1.0' 
directory='extension/anon' 
relocatable = false 
requires = 'pgcrypto' 
superuser = false 
module_pathname = '$libdir/anon' 
trusted = true
